# --- Spring Boot BOM & transitive dependencies -----------------------------
# Remediation: Spring Boot 3.5.7 -> 3.5.14 BOM bump (patch), plus a handful of
# individual libs (bouncycastle, lz4-java, commons-fileupload, postgres JDBC).
# Deferred until the W5D2 Testcontainers matrix (Postgres/Mongo/Redis/Kafka)
# is running under Compose so the bump can be validated end-to-end before it
# lands. Doing it blindly in W5D1 would change application behavior surfaces
# (Tomcat, security, Netty) without a covering integration run.

